  <exercise xml:id="ex_transformation_vector_scale">
    <title>Scalar multiplication</title>
    <statement>
      <p>
        Let <m>V</m> be a vector space. Fix <m>c\in \R</m> and define <m>T\colon V\rightarrow V</m> as <m>T(\boldv)=c\boldv</m>: <ie />, <m>T</m> is scalar multiplication by <m>c</m>. Show that <m>T</m> is a linear transformation.
      </p>
    </statement>
  </exercise>
